  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Meadows\" title=\"House Meadows\"><img alt=\"House Meadows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/House_Meadows.svg/50px-House_Meadows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/House_Meadows.svg/75px-House_Meadows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/House_Meadows.svg/100px-House_Meadows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lysa Meadows</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/50px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/75px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/100px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Meadows\" title=\"House Meadows\">House Meadows</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Olymer_Tyrell\" title=\"Olymer Tyrell\">Olymer Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Tyrell\" title=\"Raymund Tyrell\">Raymund Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Tyrell\" title=\"Rickard Tyrell\">Rickard Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Megga_Tyrell\" title=\"Megga Tyrell\">Megga Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lysa Meadows</b> is a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Meadows\" title=\"House Meadows\">House Meadows</a>. She is married to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Olymer_Tyrell\" title=\"Olymer Tyrell\">Olymer Tyrell</a> and together they have three children, <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Tyrell\" title=\"Raymund Tyrell\">Raymund</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Tyrell\" title=\"Rickard Tyrell\">Rickard</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Megga_Tyrell\" title=\"Megga Tyrell\">Megga Tyrell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lysa_Meadows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lysa's relation to <a href=\"/index.php/Elwood_Meadows\" title=\"Elwood Meadows\">Elwood Meadows</a>, the young <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Grassfield_Keep\" title=\"Lord of Grassfield Keep\">Lord of Grassfield Keep</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Meadows\" title=\"House Meadows\">House Meadows</a>, is unknown.\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Meadows\" title=\"House Meadows\">Meadows</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway\" title=\"House Fossoway\">Fossoway</a><br /><small>(possibly)</small><br /><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;Note 1&#93;</a></sup></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Lysa</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></d